   <text>
      <body>
         <div xml:lang="en" type="translation">
            <ab>Statilius Maximus to Athenodoros, strategos of the Oxyrhynchite nome, greetings. If, as you write, on the basis of a ruling given by his Excellency the prefect another three pastophoroi have been appointed in addition to those in charge of the security of the temple, then these also, like their colleagues, are entitled to receive (a share of) the police-tax. I pray for your good health. Year 20, Hadrianos 24.</ab>
